==================== Input ====================
/* a comment between a function argument and its comma stays BEFORE the comma */
a {
  color: rgb(1 /* c */, 2, 3);
  color: rgb(1, /* c */ 2, 3);
  background: url(a.png /* c */, b.png);
  width: var(--x /* c */, 10px);
  /* the kept var() trailing comma counts too */
  height: var(--y /* c */,);
  color: color-mix(in srgb /* space */, red 50% /* half */, blue);
}

==================== Output ====================
